(Arm/disarm laser into motion.probe-input via setp and2.6.in0.)
(The Laser Setter tab prefers halcmd setp; this macro is a manual fallback.)
(P1 = 1 arm, P1 = 0 disarm. Uses system MDI (halcmd) — requires allow.)

o<laser_mux_toggle> sub
    (DEBUG, LASER MUX: use the Laser Setter tab — it arms HAL around measure moves)
o<laser_mux_toggle> endsub

